WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:05.267
Now I lay me down to sleep,

00:05.338 --> 00:08.637
I pray the Lord
my soul to keep.

00:08.708 --> 00:12.007
If I die before I wake,

00:12.078 --> 00:15.377
I pray the Lord
my soul to take.

00:15.448 --> 00:19.350
God bless Mommy,
God bless Daddy,

00:19.419 --> 00:21.944
and Grandma
and Grandpa LaPierre,

00:22.022 --> 00:24.923
and Grandma
and Grandpa Jason, and...

00:24.991 --> 00:27.892
Okay, okay, Amber Lynn.
Bedtime. Come on.

00:28.962 --> 00:32.557
You grab Mike, okay?
Hop in.

00:32.631 --> 00:35.533
Let's get you cozy, cozy,
toasty, toasty.

00:35.602 --> 00:38.332
Inside. Snug as a bug.

00:38.405 --> 00:40.498
- Night-night, Lynnie.
- Night-night, Daddy.

00:41.674 --> 00:45.166
- Night, Mommy.
- Night, love.

00:46.413 --> 00:48.973
Bed lights out, Amber Lynn.

00:49.049 --> 00:51.017
Good girl.
That's a good girl.

